Name: Average resolution time following 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Completed + In Call and the end of the case

Name: Average duration from 'Completed + In Call' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total duration of 'Completed + In Call' activities in the event log
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Completed + In Call and the end of the case

Name: Average lead time before 'Completed + In Call' occurs after 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Longest duration from 'Completed + In Call' to any subsequent activity
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + In Call' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001E27CECF0A0> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest duration from any activity to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average duration from 'Completed + In Call' to 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Median duration from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Difference in average duration between 'Completed + In Call' and 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Total count of 'Completed + In Call' activities preceding 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Comparison of average duration from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + In Call' versus 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Duration variance of 'Completed + In Call' across different cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Earliest occurrence of 'Completed + In Call' after case initiation
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Completed + In Call and the end of the case

Name: Latest occurrence of 'Completed + In Call' before case closure
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + In Call' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001E27CECF0A0> - AppliesTo.PROCESS
